      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The Whites of Their Eyes\n\n\nDevelopers:\nJack LeJeune\nDaniel Martinez\nRayan
    Bounab\n\nPlayer Weapons and UI\nJack LeJeune\n\nEnemy Creation and Behavior\nDaniel
    Martinez\n\nPlayer Movement and Controls\nRayan Bounab\n\nLevel Design\nJack
    LeJeune \nRayan Bounab\n\nOriginal Concept\nJack LeJeune\n\nOutside Assets Used:\n\nSci-fi
    Guns Sfx Pack\nBy: Mikael Vanninen\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/audio/sound-fx/sci-fi-guns-sfx-pack-181144\n\nMonster
    Sound Effects Vol.1\r\nAuthor: Atelier Magicae\r\nCreator of Assests: Riria/Ririsaurus\nhttps://ateliermagicae.itch.io/monster-sound-effects-vol1\n\nAbyssal
    Horror SFX Vol.1\r\nAuthor: Atelier Magicae\r\nCreator of Assets: Riria/Ririsaurus\nhttps://ateliermagicae.itch.io/abyssal-horrors-sfx-vol1\n\nWar
    FX\r\nAuthor: Jean Moreno\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/vfx/particles/war-fx-5669\n\nGrenade
    Sound FX\r\nAuthor: MGWSoundDesin\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/audio/sound-fx/grenade-sound-fx-147490\n\nFree
    Cinematic Sound Effects\r\nAuthor: Gregor Quendel\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/p/free-cinematic-sound-effects-224972\n\nMoster
    Roar Sound Pack\nAuthor: Leonardo Calvo\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/3d/props/weapons/rusty-sword-315378\n\nRusty
    Sword\nAuthor: Danvil\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/3d/props/weapons/rusty-sword-315378\n\nModels
    and Animations:\r\nAuthor: Adobe Mixamo\nhttps://www.mixamo.com/#/?page=1&type=Character\n\nVFX
    URP - Fire Package\r\nAuthor: Cartoon VFX By Wallcoeur\nhttps://assetstore.unity.com/packages/vfx/particles/fire-explosions/vfx-urp-fire-package-305098\n\nPlayer
    Weapon Sounds:\npixabay.com/sound-effects/\nCreators: Various, free liscense\n\nGround,
    Wall, Sand Wall Textures:\npixabay.com\nCreators: Various, free liscense\n\nBurning
    Text Generator:\nhttps://cooltext.com/Logo-Design-Burning\n\n\nThank You For
    Playing!"
